\f1 \cf0 Let me break down the first Christmas:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They were poor financially \'96 the text says it\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They were poor relationally \'96 completely away from family\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They were poor present wise \'96 no gifts for the king came\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They were poor in traditions \'96 it\'92s the first one\'85all they had was \'93remember the time we had a baby in a barn?\'94  Not something you really want to dwell on.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t know what they thought of the day\'85but thousands of years later we celebrate it as one of the best days ever.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Christmas should be this celebration of what we\'92ve already been given, not what we could possible get.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It isn\'92t about this year but about that year\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It isn\'92t about what we get but what we\'92ve already been given\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It isn\'92t about all the things we make it out to be\'85but about one thing.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The gift you have is more important than the gift you give\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs40 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So this Christmas my prayer for you is that you would be able to look past all of the stuff\'85all the family drama and stress of getting the right toys or getting the right things.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You would be able to look past having to appear a certain way and sit in the presence of a God who loves you so much He sent His son for you.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 22\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When the time came for the purification rites required by the Law of Moses, Joseph and Mary took him to Jerusalem to present him to the Lord\'a0\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This whole things started because we are naturally disconnected from God\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We naturally walk father and farther away from Him.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They had a system of purification that was complex and difficult.  And most people never really knew where they were at with God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We no longer struggle with that.  We can know we are good with God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We can know, not because of us but because of Jesus\
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
